&lt;p&gt;Diagnostic Booking Co-ordinator, Cardiology, Integrated Medicine&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to appoint to one part-time band 3 post within the Cardiology Department based at Northwick Park Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic and self-motivated individual to join the team. The post holder will be responsible for booking patients requiring diagnostic tests in the cardiology department and he/she will be required to utilise the trust booking systems and support all aspects of booking process including contact with patients and teams. The role will focus on supporting a positive patient experience within the service with a key emphasis on achieving RTT/Diagnostic standards. The post holder will work closely with the service team and receive support and training as required to fulfil the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAndrew RansleyJob titleAssistant Service ManagerEmail addressandrew.ransley@nhs.netTelephone number02088693471Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Andrew Ransley, Assistant Service Manager on andrew.ransley@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
